Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.58,0:00:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创世之初 冥冥之中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}In the beginning, there was darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.92,0:00:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随着一声爆炸\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and then, bang--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.04,0:00:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诞生了无尽膨胀的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}giving birth to an endless expanding existence
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.59,0:00:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间 空间和物质\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of time, space, and matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.30,0:00:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一天 新的发现都在揭秘这个诡异\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Every day, new discoveries are unlocking the mysterious,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.84,0:00:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,震撼 神秘莫测的地方 - 我们所谓的《宇宙》\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the mind-blowing, the deadly secrets of a place we call "The Universe."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.77,0:00:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,环抱在银河系气体尘埃的旋臂中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Among the swirling gas and dust in the arms of the Milky Way,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.56,0:00:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繁星闪现 并不孤单 而是成群结队\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}stars flash into existence, not alone, but in clusters,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.90,0:00:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠引力结合在一起\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}held together by the force of gravity.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.32,0:00:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引力就像是宇宙中的雕塑家\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Gravity is like the sculptor of the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.58,0:00:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在来一次星系中的星团大巡游\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Now take a grand tour of the galaxy's star clusters,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.75,0:00:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太空宝藏图\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the treasure maps of space,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.21,0:00:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掌握着银河系里4000亿颗太阳奥秘的关键线索\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}holding critical clues to the mysteries of the Milky Way's 400 billion suns.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.13,0:00:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星团确实让我们掌握了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Star clusters really allowed us to get a handle
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.84,0:00:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恒星是如何度过一生的 以及它们的生死情况\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}on how stars go through their lives, how they live and die.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.80,0:01:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是暴戾混乱的世界 我们搜寻宇宙星团\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's a violent, chaotic existence, where our search for cosmic clusters
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.31,0:01:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能最终揭示一个永恒暗无天日的宇宙\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}may end up revealing a universe in darkness for eternity.
