Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.31,0:38:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天体就是行星 恒星 或星系\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The bodies are planets, stars, or galaxies,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.10,0:38:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题是通过一些简单的计算\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and the problem is to do some simple math
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.82,0:38:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来计算出牛顿的基本引力定律是如何\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to figure out how Isaac Newton's basic laws of gravity
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.24,0:38:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让行星或恒星在太空中运动的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}make the planets or stars move in space.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.24,0:38:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种模拟是极其强有力的手段\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Such simulations are remarkably powerful ways
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.62,0:38:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来研究复杂系统 如星系团\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to study how complex systems like clusters of galaxies
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.00,0:39:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,及星系是如何与时俱进的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and galaxies evolve with time.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.00,0:39:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼得 图本 - 马里兰大学的模拟专家\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Peter Teuben, a simulation specialist at the University of Maryland,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.26,0:39:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将引力公式编程\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}programs the gravity formulas
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.30,0:39:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了一台叫做沉思的计算机里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}into a supercomputer named Deepthought.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.68,0:39:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很容易 比如\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's easy, for instance,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.02,0:39:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要计算出行星围绕恒星的轨道\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to figure the orbit of a planet around a star.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.06,0:39:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这叫做二体问题\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That's called a two-body problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.65,0:39:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大学数学系学生立刻就可以解决\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A college math student can do it in a snap.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.94,0:39:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过想想你要计算星团里一大堆恒星的运动呢\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But suppose you have to work out the motions of a swarm of stars in a star cluster.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.86,0:39:34.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,N体问题有点像杂耍表演\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The N-body problem is a little bit like a juggling act.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.53,0:39:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你碰上二体问题 我们这里有一个球\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If you have a two-body problem, here we have one ball 
