Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.58,0:39:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道我能不能玩两个球 哎呀\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I don't know if I can do two balls. Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.04,0:39:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 显然 我玩不了两个球\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Well, clearly, I cannot do two balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.17,0:39:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要大量的尝试和大脑的演绎\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And it takes a lot of effort and interpretation by the brain
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.43,0:39:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何来正确地杂耍这两个球\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}how to correctly juggle two balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.14,0:39:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在来设想我们要来玩三个球或四个球\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Now imagine that we have to do three balls or four balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.39,0:39:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可来不了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I cannot do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.64,0:40:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人能做到的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There are people who can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.68,0:40:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过复杂性会止于某个点上\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But the complexity ends at some point.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.85,0:40:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人能玩到20个球\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Nobody can do 20 balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.69,0:40:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出人意料的是 问题背后的数学却是相当简单的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Surprisingly, the math behind the problem is fairly easy,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.49,0:40:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你需要超级计算机的原因就在于\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but the reason you need a supercomputer
