Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.49,0:40:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这纯粹是枯燥的工作 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's pure grunt work 
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.50,0:40:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 伙计们 写上你的位置\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}All right, guys, write your positions.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.96,0:40:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来看图本学生的论证\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}As Teuben's students demonstrate,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.17,0:40:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试图不用计算机来解决12颗恒星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}when trying to do it for 12 stars without a computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.13,0:40:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一颗在6-4\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Number 1 is at 6-4.
