Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.55,0:40:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三 在2-4\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Number 3. - 3 is at 2-4.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.97,0:40:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这样的计算中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}In calculations like these,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.76,0:40:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每颗星的初始位置在图标上都有了坐标\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}each star's starting position gets coordinates on a chart.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.77,0:40:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第八在4-4\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Number 8 is at 4-4.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.73,0:40:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每颗星同时有了自己的速度\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Each star also gets its own speed,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.19,0:40:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的事就取决于同学们了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and the rest is up to the students.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.78,0:40:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用牛顿定律 他们要计算出\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Using Newton's laws, they have to figure out
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.74,0:40:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每颗星的引力是如何与其它每颗星的作用\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}how each star's gravity acts on each one of the others
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.03,0:41:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来确定每颗星在下一个时间点的具体位置\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to determine where each star's position will be at the next point in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.83,0:41:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一颗\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Number 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.87,0:41:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些同学将需要不间断工作300年\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}These students would need to work for 300 years nonstop
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.04,0:41:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来完成超级计算机一秒钟所做的工作\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to do what a supercomputer can do in one second.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.72,0:41:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星系团的计算将猛增到数以百万计\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Calculations for galaxy clusters ramp up to millions,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.06,0:41:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至数十亿个N体\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}even billions of "N" bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.10,0:41:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是幸运的是 超级计算机越来越能够满足\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But fortunately, supercomputers are increasingly available
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.40,0:41:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天文学家模拟宇宙的过去 现在和将来的渴望\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to astronomers eager to simulate the past, present, and future of the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.36,0:41:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前最先进的超级计算机\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The current state-of-the-art supercomputers
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.03,0:41:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上都是现成的计算机\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}are actually off-the-shelf computers
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.07,0:41:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你我家用的台式计算机\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that you and I use at home, desktop computers.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.45,0:41:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一的事情就是我们将它们组合在一起\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The only thing is we put them all together.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.70,0:41:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们不难建起 并不昂贵\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They're easy to build, they're cheap to build,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.04,0:41:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此可以用上好多\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}so there's many available.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.59,0:41:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最复杂的趋势模拟之一\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Among the most complex of the current simulations
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.47,0:41:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是欧洲的千年运算\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is the Millennium Run in Europe,
